Package: flowr
Title: Static Dataflow Analysis and Program Slicing for R via flowR
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Florian", "Sihler", email = "florian.sihler@uni-ulm.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("flowr-analysis", role = "cph"))
Description: A robust R client for flowR, a static dataflow analyzer and program
    slicer for the R language. Connects to a flowR server over a simple,
    newline-delimited JSON protocol and can obtain that server through several
    interchangeable engines: flowR's JavaScript and WebAssembly bundle shipped
    with the package (run on 'Node.js'), a self-contained downloaded binary, a
    system or private 'Node.js' install, or 'Docker'. Supports program slicing,
    the query API and the read-eval-print loop of flowR 2.11.1.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
